:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Alciphr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.3</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: on the other hand, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καταβαλεῖν, λῦσαι, μεθεῖναι τὰς ὀ.</foreign> or <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὴν ὀ.</foreign>, let down or unknit <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the brow</tr_>, become calm or cheerful again, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg001.perseus-grc1:167\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyc.\">Cyc.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">167</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg005.perseus-grc1:290\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hipp.\">Hipp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">290</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg018.perseus-grc1:648\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IA\">IA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">648</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀ. μὴ καθειμένη</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Zeno Stoic.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.58</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σχάζεσθαι τὰς ὀ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0497.tlg001:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Pl.Com.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">32</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">καθέσθαι</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.1062f</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: the brow was also the seat of smiles and joy, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <q